Detailed Description

A wrapper to control single QDomNode-instance.

This class acts as a wrapper for QDomNode class and provides services for accessing these the nodes of an XML QDomDocument

Member Function Documentation

IPXactItem * IPXactItem::child ( int  index  ) 

Create wrapper for the child of a QDomNode.

This function creates a wrapper for a new node. IPXactModen class uses this function to help create new model indexes

Parameters:
index The index of the child to be created
Returns:
A pointer to the new instance of a IPXactItem. If the QDomNode was previously wrapped then it is returned. If the child is invalid 0 is returned. For valid children a new wrapper is constructed and stored.
